ge-franchisees-say-theyre-real-losers-restaurants-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRemember%20Thinking%20I%20Was%20Dying%26quot%3B%3A%20Salman%20Rushdie%20Recounts%202022%20Knife%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai-born%20Booker%20Prize-winning%20author%20Salman%20Rushdie%20has%20spoken%20in%20detail%20about%20the%20moment%20he%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20man%20with%20a%20knife%20on%20a%20stage%20in%20New%20York%20in%202022.%20He%20said%20he%20thought%20he%20was%20dying%20as%20his%20left%20eye%20hung%20down%20his%20face%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20soft-boiled%20egg%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20British-American%20author%20was%20on%20stage%20in%20August%202022%20when%20he%20was%20stabbed%20up%20to%2012%20times%20by%20accused%20Hadi%20Matar%20in%20prison%20for%20attempted%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20BBC%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20his%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20attack%20in%20'Knife%3A%20Meditations%20After%20an%20Attempted%20Murder'%20this%20week%2C%20the%20author%20admitted%20that%20losing%20an%20eye%20is%20something%20that%20%26quot%3Bupsets%20me%20every%20day%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20memoir%20was%20his%20way%20of%20fighting%20back%20against%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20thought%20he%20punched%20me%20very%20hard.%20I%20didn't%20realise%20it%20was%20a%20knife%20in%20his%20hand%2C%20and%20then%20I%20saw%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20I%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20weapon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rushdie%2C%20recalling%20the%20moment%20of%20the%20attack%20at%20the%20Chautauqua%20Institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20was%20just%20slashing%20wildly%20at%20everything.%20So%2C%20there%20was%20a%20very%20big%20slash%20across%20my%20neck%20and%20stab%20wounds%20down%20by%20the%20middle%20of%20my%20torso%20and%20two%20to%20the%20side%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20the%20wound%20in%