he%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%20bowling%20the%20last%20over%20showed%20the%20lack%20of%20faith%20on%20Akash%20madhwal's%20bowling%20and%20his%20own%20lack%20of%20skill%20as%20a%20death%20over%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Irfan%20Pathan%20(%40IrfanPathan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIrfanPathan%2Fstatus%2F1779569415962644822%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20and%20Kevin%20Pietersen%20also%20questioned%20Hardik's%20captaincy%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20absolutely%20ordinary%20bowling%2C%20ordinary%20captaincy.%20They%20should%20have%20been%20restricted%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20had%20batted%20so%20well%20along%20with%20Shivam%20Dube.%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20they%20should%20have%20been%20restricted%20to%20185-190%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%20the%20worst%20kind%20of%20bowling%20that%20I've%20seen%20for%20a%20long%2C%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports%20during%20the%20innings%20break%20after%20CSK%20posted%20206%20for%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20almost%20looks%20like%20I've%20had%20this%20embrace%20with%20my%20hero.%20I've%20got%20the%20kind%20of%20deliveries%20that%20he's%20gonna%20hit%20for%20sixes.%20One%20six%20is%20fine.%20The%20next%20one%20is%20a%20length%20ball%20when%20you%20know%20this%20batter%20is%20hunting%20for%20a%20length%20ball%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThird%20ball%20is%20again%20a%20full%20toss%20on%20the%20legs%20when%20you%20know%20he%20(Dhoni)%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20six.%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20finished%20with%20figures%20of%202%20for%2043%20from%20his%20four%20overs%20and%20also%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20with%20the%20b