re%20ingredients%2C%20typically%20things%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20find%20in%20a%20domestic%20kitchen.%20They%20usually%20have%20a%20long%20shelf%20life%2C%20come%20in%20highly%20marketed%20packaging%2C%20and%20are%20made%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-research-explains-why-cant-stop-eating-chips-ice-cream-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultra-palatable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hobson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20a%20book%20on%20UPFs%2C%20he%20realized%20how%20much%20of%20what%20we%20eat%20is%20considered%20highly%20processed%2C%20from%20obvious%20items%20like%20potato%20chips%2C%20to%20more%20surprising%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-bread-recipes-more-nutrient-dense-nuts-fruits-vegetables-dietitians-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutrient-dense%20foods%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuch%20as%20store-bought%20wholewheat%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Hobson%20focuses%20on%20eating%20whole%20foods%20and%20cooking%20from%20scratch%20when%20he%20can.%20However%2C%20he%20stressed%20that%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20and%20unnecessary%20to%20cut%20out%20UPFs%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20about%20cutting%20down%20rather%20than%20getting%20too%20paranoid%20and%20trying%20to%20cut%20everything%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20only%20do%20what%20you%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHobson%20shared%20what%20he%20used%20to%20eat%20for%20dinner%20before%20he%20made%20the%20change%20to%20his%20diet%20and%20what%20he%20eats%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStore-bought%20pasta%20sauces%20and%20marinades%20can%20be%20processed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20dinner%2C%20Hobson%20would%20often%20make%20a%20one-pot%20dish%20such%20as%20pasta%2C%20curry%2C%20or%20stew.%20He'd%20typically%20use%20a%20premade%20sauce%20or%20marinade%20from%20the%20store%2C%20which%20are%20usually%20ultra-processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20was%20making%20spaghetti%20Bolognese%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he'd%20use%20a%20premade%20tomato%20pasta%20sauce%2C%20which%20might%20contain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffood-additives%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadditives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20he%20might%20buy%20chicken%20that%20comes%20in%20an%20ultra-processed%20sauce%20or%20marinade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he's%20gotten%20into%20the%20habit%20of%20making%20sauces%20and%20seasonings%20from%20scratch.%20And%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20take%20long%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20can%20whip%20up%20a%20cajun%20spice%20seasoning%20to%20coat%20his%20chicken%20within%20seconds%20by%20mixing%20ground%20cumin%2C%20coriander%2C%20and%20paprika%20together.%20Or%20make%20a%20tomato%20sauce%20using%20canned%20tomatoes%2C%20which%20are%20processed%20rather%20than%20ultra-processed.%20He%20makes%20a%20big%20batch%20and%20puts%20some%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20marinating%20chicken%20with%20his%20hands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661cf5b716bde8d4ead8d6a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHobson%20can%20whip%20up%20a%20chicken%20seasoning%20in%20minutes.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EQuick%20meals%20and%20batch-cooking%20can%20make%20eating%20fewer%20UPFs%20easier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHobson%20is%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmeal-prepping-how-to-stay-on-track-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatch%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20saves%20him%20time%20and%20prevents%20him%20from%20ordering%20takeout%20when%20he's%20hungry.%20He%20will%20often%20defrost%20a%20dish%20he's%20made%20in%20bulk%20and%20have%20it%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20UPFs%20is%20that%20they%20are%20convenient%2C%20Hobson%20said.%20So%20%26quot%3Bit's%20really%20nice%20when%20I%20know%20that%20I've%20got%20stuff%20in%20the%20freezer%20and%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20cooking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20times%20when%20this%20isn't%20possible%2C%20he%20leans%20on%20quick%20meals%20such%20as%20egg-fried%20rice%20with%20vegetables.%20To%20make%20it%2C%20he%20adds%20some%20microwave%20rice%20to%20a%20pan%20and%20cracks%20two%20eggs.%20Once%20the%20eggs%20have%20set%2C%20he%20mixes%20them%20into%20the%20rice%20and%20adds%20soy%20sauce%20and%20either%20some%20frozen%20peas%2C%20frozen%20sweet%20corn%2C%20or%20spinach%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20he%20has%20at%20home.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20super%2C%20super%20quick%2C%20and%20super%20nutritious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20just%20finding%20little%20ways%20to%20make%20food%20that%20doesn't%20take%20too%20much%20time%2C%20but%20then%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20you%20are%20relying%20on%20a%20UPF%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutritionist-cut-down-on-ultra-processed-foods-dinner-before-after-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713174194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616b4231caec1275a6e8a46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutritionist-cut-down-on-ultra-processed-foods-dinner-before-after-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nutritionist%20Rob%20Hobson%20avoids%20ultra-processed%20foods%20after%20learning%20about%20the%20potential%20health%20risks.%20Here's%20what%20he%20eats%20for%20dinner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutritionist-cut-down-on-ultra-processed-foods-dinner-before-after-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Jordan%2C%20Which%20Slammed%20Israel%20Over%20Gaza%2C%20Stepped%20In%20To%20Stop%20Iran%20Drones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Iran%20fired%20over%20300%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20Arab-majority%20Jordan%20joined%20Israel's%20allies%20in%20intercepting%20them.%20The%20development%2C%20arguably%20as%20surprising%20as%20Iran's%20first%20direct%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Jordan's%20strong%20criticism%20of%20the%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20dispensation%20for%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20that%20has%20left%20over%2033%2C000%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20by%20King%20Abdullah%20II%2C%20which%20has%20been%20panned%20by%20pro-Palestine%20voices%2C%20is%20in%20effect%20a%20delicate%20balancing%20act%20by%20a%20militarily%20weak%20and%20poor%20country%20that%20cannot%20risk%20war%20with%20its%20neighbour.%20In%20its%20official%20statement%2C%20Jordan%20said%20it%20shot%20down%20the%20Iranian%20drones%20in%20an%20act%20of%20self-defence%20and%20not%20to%20help%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWar%20And%20Peace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJordan%20was%20among%20the%20Arab%20League%20countries%20that%20invaded%20the%20former%20Palestinian%20Mandate%20territory%20in%201948%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20recommending%20a%20plan%20to%20partition%20the%20territory%20into%20an%20Arab%20state%2C%20a%20Jewish%20state%20and%20the%20City%20of%20Jerusalem.%20After%20the%20war%2C%20Jordan%20was%20in%20control%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20formally%20annexed%20the%20territories%20in%201950.%20About%2020%20years%20later%2C%20in%201967%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Israel%20were%20again%20on%20opposite%20sides%20in%20the%20Six%20Day%20War%20and%20Amman%20lost%20control%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Jerusalem%20to%20Israel.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20signed%20a%20peace%20treaty%20with%20Israel%20in%201994%2C%20the%20second%20Arab%20country%20after%20Egypt%20to%20do%20so.%20This%20was%20after%20the%201993%20Oslo%20Accords%20--%20a%20peace%20process%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organization%20led%20by%20Yasser%20Arafat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20peace%20treaty%20in%20place%2C%20Israel%20and%20Jordan%20opened%20their%20borders.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20the%20309-km%20border%20Israel%20shares%20with%20Jordan%20is%20its%20quietest.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20deploys%20just%20three%20battalions%20on%20this%20border%2C%20significant%20in%20a%20heavily%20militarised%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael-Jordan%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJordan's%20economy%20ranks%2089th%20in%20the%20world%20by%20GDP.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20treaty%20promoted%20by%20the%20US%2C%20it%20has%20Qualified%20Industrial%20Zones%20for%20companies%20that%20use%20Israeli%20inputs.%20These%20companies%20can%20export%20their%20products%20duty-free%20to%20the%20US%20and%20have%20generated%2036%2C000%20jobs%20over%20the%20years%20--%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20a%20country%20with%20a%20population%20of%20just%20over%20a%20crore.%20The%20Muslim%20Brotherhood's%20demands%20that%20the%20government%20shut%20down%20these%20zones%20have%20elicited%20a%20simple%20reply%3A%20they%20provide%20jobs.%20Jordan%20is%20also%20among%20the%20biggest%20recipients%20of%20aid%20from%20US%2C%20Israel's%20strong%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%2C%20however%2C%20have%20not%20stopped%20Amman%20from%20hitting%20out%20at%20Israel%20over%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20Gaza%20issue.%20Amid%20Israel's%20counterstrike%20on%20Hamas%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20King%20Abdullah%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Bcollective%20punishment%26quot%3B%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20Jordan%20also%20accused%20Israel%20of%20creating%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%26quot%3B%20and%20recalled%20its%20ambassador%20from%20Tel%20Aviv.%20The%20king%20also%20pushed%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20and%20appealed%20to%20Western%20leaders%20to%20back%20the%20cause.%20This%20political%20position%2C%20despite%20strong%20trade%20links%2C%20is%20a%20tightrope%20walk%20by%20Amman%20to%20balance%20its%20economic%20interests%20and%20the%20sentiments%20of%20a%20significant%20Palestinian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Balancing%20Act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20Iran's%20drone%20strikes%2C%20King%20Abdullah%20had%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20Iranians%20%26quot%3Bto%20play%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20territory%20as%20they%20do%20in%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%20and%20Lebanon%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Farticle%2Fbjcapncxa%5C%22%3EYnet%20news%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Arab%20media%20outlets%20and%20to%20a%20Jordanian%20newspaper%2C%20Abdullah%20expressed%20his%20discontent%20with%20the%20Iranian%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20directing%20pro-Iran%20militias%20in%20Iraq%20against%20Jordan.%20Amman%20has%20seen%20the%20cost%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20have%20paid%2C%20so%20wants%20stability%20within%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Iran%20fired%20its%20volley%20of%20missiles%20and%20drones%2C%20King%20Abdullah%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20was%20working%20with%20his%20military%20and%20intelligence%20for%20a%20swift%20response.%20Its%20planes%20took%20off%20to%20shoot%20down%20drones%20targeting%20Israel.%20Tel%20Aviv%20later%20said%20that%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20drones%20were%20shot%20down%20before%20they%20reached%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20the%20CNN%2C%20Jordan's%20foreign%20minister%20Ayman%20Safadi%20said%20the%20focus%20now%20is%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20that%20is%20to%20end%20the%20%26quot%3Baggression%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Billegal%20measures%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20get%20on%20a%20track%20that%20will%20produce%20%26quot%3Blasting%20peace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20intercepting%20Iranian%20drones%20aimed%20at%20Israel%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20range%20of%20fire.%20Any%20missile%20or%20projectile%20that%20could%20fall%20in%20Jordan%20will%20cause%20harm%20to%20Jordan%2C%20so%20we%20did%20what%20we%20have%20to%20do.%20Let%20me%20be%20very%20clear.%20We%20will%20do%20the%20same%20regardless%20of%20where%20those%20drones%20are%20from%2C%20from%20Israel%2C%20from%20Iran%2C%20from%20anybody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jordan's%20response%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20surprise%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20their%20relations%20would%20be%20premature.%20It%20is%20rooted%20more%20in%20Amman's%20necessities%20than%20in%20a%20diplomatic%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20sparked%20strong%20criticism%20of%20King%20Abdullah.%20A%20meme%20of%20the%20king%20in%20Israeli%20military%20uniform%20has%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713174180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fg112uca_jordan-king-and-bibi_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-israel-jordan-relations-why-jordan-which-slammed-israel-over-gaza-stepped-in-to-stop-iran-drones-5445958%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Iran%20fired%20over%20300%20drones%20and%20missiles%20at%20Israel%2C%20Arab-majority%20Jordan%20joined%20Tel%20Aviv's%20allies%20in%20intercepting%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-conflict-israel-jordan-relations-why-jordan-which-slammed-israel-over-gaza-stepped-in-to-stop-iran-drones-5445958%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppro