r%20MI%20lost%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20by%2020%20runs%20in%20their%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20match.%20CSK%20legend%20MS%20Dhoni%20took%2026%20runs%20off%20Pandya's%20final%20over%20with%20the%20help%20of%20three%20consecutive%20sixes%20as%20the%20MI%20skipper%20struggled%20for%20right%20line%20and%20length%20while%20also%20bowling%20two%20wides%20at%20a%20crucial%20time.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fpoints-table%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIPL%202024%20Points%20Table%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20finished%20with%20figures%20of%202%20for%2043%20from%20his%20four%20overs%20and%20also%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20managing%20a%20mere%20two%20runs%20off%20six%20balls%20at%20a%20crucial%20juncture%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou're%20going%20to%20have%20those%20days.%20I'm%20sick%20and%20fed%20up%20of%20just%20looking%20to%20pinpoint%20at%20individuals.%20Cricket%20is%20a%20team%20sport%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Pandya)%20is%20a%20confident%20guy.%20He%20has%20been%20great%20around%20the%20group.%20In%20cricket%2C%20you%20have%20good%20days%20and%20you%20have%20bad%20days.%20I'm%20seeing%20an%20individual%20who's%20working%20bloody%20hard%20to%20continue%20his%20skill%20and%20to%20ply%20his%20trade.%E2%80%9D%20Pollard%20reminded%20fans%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20Pandya%20being%20picked%20for%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20campaign%2C%20saying%20if%20that%20happens%20everyone%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98singing%20his%20praises'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20individual%20that's%20going%20to%20represent%20the%20country%20in%20less%20than%20six%20weeks'%20time.%20We're%20all%20going%20to%20be%20cheering%20for%20him%20and%20want%20him%20to%20do%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20West%20Indian%20who%20himself%20is%20a%20MI%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20high%20time%20that%20we%20try%20to%20encourage%20and%20try%20to%20stop%20nitpick.%20See%20if%20we%20can%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20one%20of%20the%20great%20all-rounders%20India%20could%20ever%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20can%20bat%2C%20he%20can%20bowl%2C%20he%20can%20field.%20He%20has%20an%20X%20factor%20about%20him.%20I%20hope%20very%20well%20deep%20down%20within%20my%20heart%20that%20when%20he%20comes%20out%20on%20top%2C%20I'll%20sit%20back%20and%20I'll%20watch%20everyone%20sing%20his%20praises.%E2%80%9D%20The%20match%20witnessed%20intermittent%20booing%20of%20Pandya%20who%20struggled%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball%20and%20also%20received%20criticism%20from%20former%20England%20captain%20Kevin%20Pietersen%20who%20claimed%20that%20the%20MI%20skipper%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98smiling%20too%20much'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPollard%20said%20he%20is%20seeing%20Pandya%20evolving%20and%20backed%20him%20to%20turn%20things%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20individual%2C%20you%20have%20to%20evolve%20as%20well.%20When%20you're%20young%20and%20there's%20that%20youthful%20exuberance%2C%20you%20go%20out%20and%20you%20do%20things%20in%20a%20certain%20manner.%20But%20the%20older%20that%20you%20get%2C%20at%20times%2C%20responsibility%20sort%20of%20kicks%20in%2C%20accountability%20to%20teams%20sort%20of%20kicks%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I'm%20seeing%20is%20a%20guy%20that%20is%20evolving.%20Obviously%2C%20we%20as%20individuals%2C%20we%20want%20to%20see%20certain%20things%2C%20but%20sometimes%20the%20game%20does%20not%20demand%20certain%20things.%E2%80%9D%20Pollard%20said%20while%20Mumbai%20Indians%20would%20revisit%20their%20plans%20on%20Dhoni%20but%20added%20that%20anyone%20could%20have%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20former%20CSK%20skipper's%20onslaught%2C%20like%20Pandya%20experienced%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20he%20hit%20three%20sixes%2C%2020%20runs%2C%20some%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20over%2C%20but%20anyone%20could%20have%20gone%20for%2020%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20over%20as%20well.%20MS%20has%20been%20world-class%20for%20years%20upon%20years.%20We%20love%20to%20see%20him%20on%20the%20cricket%20field%2C%20walking%20out%20into%20stadiums.%20We're%20all%20in%20awe%20of%20what%20he%20has%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scoreline%20(20%20runs)%2C%20that's%20the%20difference.%20But%20cricket%20is%20much%20more%20than%20what%20we%20see%20at%20the%20end.%20For%20us%2C%20it's%20much%20deeper%20than%20that.%20We're%20going%20to%20dissect%20and%20we%20have%20done%20before%20throughout%20the%20tournament%20and%20do%20our%20homework%20and%20try%20to%20come%20back%20better%20as%20a%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pollard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMS%20Dhoni%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%E2%80%A6%20you%20have%20plans%20of%20how%20you%20want%20to%20bowl%20to%20them%2C%20and%20you%20go%20back%20and%20you%20look%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20executed%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713167880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvs4dcbeo_ms-dhoni-and-pollard-bcci_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fyes-ms-dhoni-hit-3-sixes-but-kieron-pollards-stunning-game-changer-remark-in-mis-defeat-5444497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni's%2020%20runs%20off%204%20balls%20was%20termed%20by%20many%20as%20the%20'game-changing'%20part%20as%20Mumbai%20Indians%20suffered%20a%20defeat%20by%2020%20runs%20against%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C