the%20special%20bride.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjanhvi-kapoor-and-boyfriend-shikhar-pahariya-get-goofy-in-new-unseen-pictures-from-radhika-merchants-bridal-shower%2Farticleshow%2F109306216.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOur%20Young%20Wicketkeeper%26quot%3B%3A%20Dhoni%20Receives%20Sensational%20Praise%20From%20Gaikwad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20could%20not%20hide%20his%20appreciation%20for%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni's%20tactical%20acumen%20following%20his%20team's%2020-run%20loss%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%20While%20Dhoni's%20barrage%20of%20three%20sixes%20and%20a%20hurriedly-completed%20two%20runs%20off%20the%20fourth%20and%20last%20delivery%20was%20something%20that%20gave%20CSK%20the%20winning%20cushion%2C%20it%20was%20the%20former%20India%20skipper's%20reading%20of%20the%20game%20from%20behind%20the%20stumps%20that%20Pandya%20felt%20made%20the%20difference%20on%20a%20belter%20of%20a%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(CSK)%20were%20smart%20with%20their%20plans%20and%20used%20the%20longer%20boundary%20well.%20They%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20it%20and%20they%20have%20a%20man%20behind%20the%20stumps%20telling%20them%20what's%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pandya%20after%20his%20side%20failed%20to%20chase%20206%20despite%20Rohit%20Sharma%20smashing%20his%20second%20IPL%20century%20and%20batting%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20gave%20Dhoni%20a%20huge%20compliment%2C%20saying%20his%20power-hitting%20with%20just%20four%20balls%20remaining%20made%20the%20difference%20between%20victory%20and%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%2C%2042%2C%20scored%2020%20off%20four%20deliveries%2C%20which%20in%20the%20end%20made%20the%20difference%20to%20the%20match's%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20young%20wicketkeeper%20(MSD)%20scoring%20three%20sixes%20down%20the%20order%20helped%20a%20lot%20and%20I%20think%20that%20was%20the%20difference.%20To%20start%20off%2C%20on%20this%20kind%20of%20ground%2C%20you%20need%2010-15%20extra%20runs.%20We%20were%20looking%20at%20215-220%2C%20but%20Bumrah%20bowled%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20captaincy%20duties%20from%20Dhoni%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBowling-wise%2C%20we%20were%20spot-on%20with%20our%20execution.%20Even%20in%20powerplay%2C%20I%20would%20have%20taken%20six%20overs%20for%2060.%20These%20kinds%20of%20venues%20demand%20both%20skills%3A%20batting%20and%20bowling.%20Our%20(Lasith)%20Malinga%20(Matheesha%20Pathirana)%20bowled%20exceptionally%20well%20and%20nailed%20those%20yorkers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20he%20did%20not%20open%20the%20innings%20and%20instead%20sent%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20with%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20Gaikwad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%2C%20Jinks%20(Rahane)%20was%20carrying%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20niggle.%20Thought%20it%20was%20better%20for%20him%20to%20open%20and%20get%20away%20quick%20runs.%20I'm%20fine%20batting%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%2C%20Pathirana%2C%20who%20grabbed%20his%20best%20IPL%20figures%20of%204%2F28%2C%20said%20he%20was%20a%20bit%20nervous%20as%20he%20was%20coming%20back%20into%20the%20side%20after%20recovering%20from%20a%20niggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20bowled%20in%20powerplay%2C%20I%20was%20nervous.%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20results%20and%20I%20just%20think%20about%20execution.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20I%20was%20having%20a%20niggle%20before%20two%20weeks%20and%20all%20support%20staff%20and%20players%20helped%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20main%20thing%20to%20have%20my%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%2C%2