%20him%20about%20the%20fandom's%20love%20for%20vampire-like%20characters%2C%20and%20he%20agrees%20they%20are%20%3Cem%3Eso%3C%2Fem%3E%20back%20in%20the%20limelight.%20Mercer%20also%20voices%20a%20vampire%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Legend%20of%20Vox%20Machina%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon-backed%20animated%20series%20he%20created%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-dungeons-dragons-sold-out-live-show-wembley-arena-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20friends%20at%20Critical%20Role.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20definitely%20embodies%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20classic%20fantasy%2C%20media-informed%20kind%20of%20antihero%20protagonist%20vampires%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20thinks%20the%20essence%20of%20a%20vampire's%20allure%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20tragedy%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bsteeped%20in%20its%20own%20mythology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20plucked%20from%20the%20cycle%20of%20life%2C%20and%20to%20subsist%20and%20exist%20is%20to%20feast%20on%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20very%20vibe%20itself%20is%20tragic%20and%20romantic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20very%20much%20borrows%20that%20aesthetic%20of%20'the%20monster%20within%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20'I%20try%20to%20be%20as%20good%20as%20I%20can%2C%20but%20there's%20something%20dark%20inside%20me%20that%20I'm%20ever%20having%20to%20keep%20at%20bay.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20%26quot%3Bwild%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20says%2C%20to%20be%20immortalized%20in%20a%20game%20like%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20me%20he%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20series%2C%20played%20early%20versions%20of%20the%20game%2C%20and%20cosplayed%20characters%20from%20it%2C%20so%20clinching%20this%20role%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20whale%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent's%20kind%20of%20emerging%20from%20his%20cave%2C%20shaking%20off%20the%20dust%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20learning%20how%20to%20be%20social%2C%20and%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20shell%20of%20self-loathing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlaying%20that%20subtle%20arc%20and%20the%20slow%20opening%20of%20that%20cold%20exterior%20has%20been%20a%20fun%20journey%20to%20explore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVideo%20games'%20vampire%20boyfriends%20are%20also%20a%20lesson%20in%20vulnerability%20%E2%80%94%20and%20navigating%20trauma%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20actor%20Neil%20Newbon%20and%20his%20character%20from%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%203%2C%26quot%3B%20Astarion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618a1cd1caec1275a6f6429%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20BAFTA-nominated%20Neil%20Newbon%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20Astarion.%3Cp%3EScott%20Garfitt%2FBAFTA%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Larian%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20caught%20up%20with%20Newbon%2C%20who's%20won%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastarion-voice-actor-neil-newbon-win-best-performance-game-awards-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20accolades%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Astarion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20beautiful%2C%20200-something-year-old%20vampire%20who's%20captured%20the%20hearts%20of%20many%20a%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%203%26quot%3B%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tough%20to%20navigate%20the%20pain%20written%20into%20Astarion's%20harrowing%20vampire-origin%20story%2C%20Newbon%20told%20me.%20Because%20there%20are%20several%20ways%20Astarion's%20character%20arc%20can%20play%20out%20based%20on%20player%20choices%2C%20Newbon%20says%20those%20who%20befriend%20the%20vampire%20in-game%20get%20to%20see%20him%20%26quot%3Bshake%20off%20a%20