man%20has%20been%20the%20conservancy.%20But%20credit%20Namgail%20for%20leading%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20unique%20endeavour%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20this%2C%20and%20he%20says%20he%20owes%20his%20success%20to%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20I%20took%20over%20as%20director%20in%202013%2C%20I%20remember%20accompanying%20Mr%20Rinchen%20to%20the%20villages%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20speaking%20to%20the%20locals.%20He%20was%20a%20great%20visionary.%20We%20would%20conduct%20numerous%20surveys%20to%20check%20on%20the%20mountain%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20lovely%20experience%20to%20learn%20from%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20college%20days%2C%20I%20would%20lead%20the%20tourists%20into%20the%20mountains%20during%20the%20summer.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Mr%20Rinchen%20was%20working%20on%20some%20projects%20for%20the%20International%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20met%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namgail%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20Wangchuk%2C%20he%20says.%20In%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20a%20simple%20afternoon%20conversation%20between%20a%20young%20college%20boy%20and%20his%20idol%20blossomed%20into%20a%20beautiful%20friendship.%20Little%20did%20Namgail%20know%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332940%2Fdevpur-royal-homestay-darbargadh-in-kutch-jadeja-family-runs-farmstay-cbse-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaton%20of%20the%20conservancy%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20pass%20to%20him%20after%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Namgail%20set%20out%20to%20head%20the%20conservancy%2C%20the%20intent%20was%20to%20substitute%20the%20fear%20the%20locals%20had%20for%20this%20beast%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20its%20ecological%20importance.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20snow%20leopard%20is%20vital%20from%20three%20standpoints%20%E2%80%94%20ecological%2C%20cultural%20and%20economic.%E2%80%9D%20For%20a%20community%20that%20views%20livestock%20as%20subsistence%2C%20losing%20it%20to%20the%20snow%20leopard%20is%20tragic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20says%20Namgail%2C%20what%20the%20people%20failed%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20the%20feline%20is%20integral%20to%20promoting%20plant%20regeneration%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20enhancing%20herbivore%20diversity%20and%20preventing%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCvRYOlSyzrA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCvRYOlSyzrA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCvRYOlSyzrA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Snow